items.headline: Welcome to the Jurassic Park Fanon Wiki!
items.desc:
WELCOME TO THE JURASSIC PARK FANON WIKI

The Jurassic Park Fanon Wiki is a place where you can build up and write your Jurassic Park inspired fan fiction or movie, or just your story about you and Jurassic Park. Anyone can create a fan fiction, but don't edit others' unless absolutely necessary, as it isn't your story.
